(14, 3, 0, 'Home Page', '', '2012-02-28 01:41:55', '2013-04-21 10:44:02', '<h2>Davidoff Hutcher &amp; Citron LLP</h2>\r\n<div class="clear">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="home-content-row">\r\n<div class="col-left cleartop">\r\n<p>Davidoff Hutcher &amp; Citron LLP was established in 1975 and has developed into a multidiscipline, full-service practice that handles legal and lobbying matters, from the routine to the complex. The firm''s experience in traditional legal services and government relations enables us to address each client''s specific concerns with a perspective and approach simply not offered by most other New York firms.</p>\r\n<p><a href="../index/firm-profile">More about our firm &gt;</a></p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="col-right cleartop">\r\n<h3>Meet The Named Partners</h3>\r\n<p style="margin-top: 0px; padding-top: 0px;"><img src="images/dhc-partners.jpg" alt="DHC Legal Partners" border="0" /></p>\r\n<p class="about-partners">Behind a tremendously successful law firm is a dedication to excellence that starts with the firm''s senior partners. Meet Larry Hutcher, Sid Davidoff and Jeffrey Citron.</p>\r\n<p align="right"><a href="contactus">Contact Us</a></p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="home-content-row noborder">\r\n<div class="col-left">\r\n<h3>Meet Our Attorneys</h3>\r\n<p>Our firm has a long standing history of delivering elegant service that permeates every facet of our legal process from the first visit to the law firm to the eventual outcome of the case. You can expect our firm to handle each aspect of your case with care and consideration, and you will feel the experience that our staff has from its combined years of handling legal endeavors.</p>\r\n<p>We are Davidoff Hutcher &amp; Citron, and with that name comes the comfort and security of knowing that from our senior partners down to our legal associates you will be in excellent hands. We invite you to meet our attorneys.</p>\r\n<p><a href="../attorneys">Meet Our Attorneys &gt;</a></p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="col-right">\r\n<h3>The latest news from the firm.</h3>\r\n<p align="center"><img src="images/dhc-news.jpg" alt="News" border="0" /></p>\r\n<p>THOMAS MOHEN JOINS DAVIDOFF HUTCHER &amp; CITRON LLP</p>\r\n<p><a href="../articles/news">Read more &gt;</a></p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 'legal, consultancies', 0x6c6567616c20616e6420636f6e73756c74616e6379, 1, 10, 0, 1, 'Home-Page', 1, ''),
