(103, 2, 0, 'Larry Hutcher as "Litigator of the Week"', '', '2013-04-18 00:00:00', '2013-04-26 06:44:05', '<p>Larry Hutcher, Co-Managing Partner and Chair of Davidoff Hutcher &amp; Citron&rsquo;s litigation group was spotlighted in&nbsp;<em>The AmLaw Litigation Daily</em>&nbsp;as &ldquo;Litigator of the Week.&rdquo;&nbsp; Larry and his client, Adam Victor, are responsible for one of the biggest legal stories of the year, revealing, what they alleged to be, DLA Piper&rsquo;s practice of &ldquo;intentional fraudulent overbilling&rdquo; and providing supporting evidence with internal emails that set the legal world on fire.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p align="LEFT"><a href="../../../app/webroot/img/gallery/File/AMLaw.pdf"><img src="../../../files/download-pdf.png" alt="" width="245" height="50" /></a></p>\r\n<p></p>', 'American Lawyer, Litigator', '', 0, 1, 1, 1, 'Larry-Hutcher-as-"Litigator-of-the-Week"', 0, ''),
